ResBaz Sydney 2023

Tue 26-Thu 28 September 2023

About ResBaz

Conference

ResBaz Sydney 2023 will be a face-to-face event hosted by the University of Sydney on Tuesday 26-Thursday 27 September 2023. The program will feature keynotes, workshops, short talks, demonstrations and lots of opportunities to find out about next gen tech and tools for researchers. Watch this space for program updates and announcements!

For examples of the sorts of training which ResBaz offers, you can visit the 2021 programme.
